examples of how stores in her territory should be set up and sends them (via the VisorPhone) to her 
headquarters in live time. For example, her bosses were planning a presentation and asked that she 
take a picture of a merchandiser and send it. The photo was taken in Illinois at about 10:30 a.m., 
and her corporate headquarters in Rhode Island had it by 11:00 a.m.<br><br>
When my wife had to be out of town on a business trip during our daughter's graduation from fifth 
grade, I was able to take pictures of our daughter's graduation and email them to my wife within 
twenty minutes of the ceremony. As you can see, with the addition of the modules we have purchased, 
our Visor handhelds have allowed us to better organize our busy lives.</font>
